SYMM -y, x, z+1/4
SYMM  y,-x, z+3/4
SFAC C H N O
UNIT 110.00 100.00 10.00 10.00
REM  CrysAlisPro recorded range (K): Min=100.0; max=100.0; aver:100.0
TEMP -173
TREF
HKLF 4
END
